to some young men then ... this was an exciting life, driving a whiskey car. it was an adventure. somebody who transported liquor and drove a hot car was kind of a hero to some people.''
hudson was about a block from his parents' house when someone pulled beside him and fired a .410-gauge shotgun through the passenger window of his car, hitting him in the head
investigators suspected a moonshine connection
